stories.title: England race to seven-wicket victory
stories.subTitle: England v India, NatWest Challenge, 1st match
stories.summary: It was always going to take something spectacular to extract England's one-day team from their recent slough of despond, and so it proved at Trent Bridge, as India were overwhelmed by seven wickets in the opening match of the NatWest Challenge
